sequenceDiagram
    participant Parent as Parent Page
    participant Module as module.js (CDN)
    participant App as Vue App

    Parent->>Module: &lt;script src=".../module.js"&gt;
    Parent->>Module: initWippyApp(AppConfig, container)
    Note over Module: No PostMessage handshake needed<br/>config provided directly
    Module->>App: init Pinia, Router, Theme
    Module->>App: app.mount(container)
